{"word":"G886 - ἀχειροποίητος - acheiropoíētos - akh-i-rop-oy'-ay-tos - Made without hands","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀχειροποίητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">acheiropoíētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">akh-i-rop-oy'-ay-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Made without hands</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கைவேலையில்லாத, கையால் செய்யப்படாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not made with hands"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5499 - χειροποίητος - cheiropoíētos - khi-rop-oy'-ay-tos/5499\">G5499</a>; <i>unmanufactured</i>, that is, <i>inartificial:</i> - made without (not made with) hands.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5495/5495\">G5495</a>, <a href=\"#/G5496/5496\">G5496</a>, <a href=\"#/G5497/5497\">G5497</a>, <a href=\"#/G5498/5498\">G5498</a>, <a href=\"#/G5499/5499\">G5499</a>, <a href=\"#/G5500/5500\">G5500</a>, <a href=\"#/G886/886\">G886</a>"}]}